{"tid":517990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人工島鋼筒 急速沉降 議員促召開特別會議討論","createTime":"2018-01-03T00:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T01:53:31.000Z","uid":32577,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"4b2c8d12a5a5a96d217fec928e3b409d777c5a86","tid":517990,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T00:22:38.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】本報昨日獨家報道港珠澳大橋香港段填海地出現急劇的不正常沉降，有顧問評估香港口岸人工島兩個填海用鋼圓筒過去一年下沉約五十至八十厘米，較路政署估計每年一厘米沉降速度快數十倍，但該署仍堅稱只下沉廿多厘米，屬「估算之內」。有立法會議員要求盡快召開特別會議討論事件，要求政府官員出席並公開有關的沉降水平顧問報告。至於當局一直強調大橋去年底「具備通車條件」，如今「限期」已過，該署回應時僅指三地政府將報請中央確定港珠澳大橋開通時間，有定案後將盡快公布。"},{"pid":"fb45068e2fac7dd5ca3f0799f54ec14a2fba7120","tid":517990,"uid":2002,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T00:48:25.000Z","msg":"拆左再起過咪得<br />\n驚咩"},{"pid":"dde9262e6fbc7d0240e2dff34058cf433bd51e70","tid":517990,"uid":49,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T00:50:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1933cdb89638f95f0dd40f7e7c518eee8e9be786","tid":517990,"uid":55913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T00:51:02.000Z","msg":"沒事兒 沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6becd96a1fe1e26151f8eb41b87cc5db13f9ce","tid":517990,"uid":1060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T00:54:43.000Z","msg":"欲速則不達"},{"pid":"cf5b3ba01f41d09b6dfbe2b3bf44aa38066b15df","tid":517990,"uid":22989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T00:59:32.000Z","msg":"工程長做長有<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e3620bab954ee02a084f6250a6ee4954915e4f3","tid":517990,"uid":47674,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T01:04:30.000Z","msg":"先撥款 後商討<br />\n先通車 後解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2375900052dc91cdd59e5ebf8c9bd13e2f50012d","tid":517990,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score"